\begin_layout Subsection
Delivering odorants: olfactometer design 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
There exists a variety of methods of delivering odorants.
 Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:olfactometer-zoo"

\end_inset

 shows a sample of the zoo of olfactometers (devices for delivering odorants)
 that have been developed to deliver odorants in experimental preparations.
 While the full assortment of olfactometers is too rich to comprehensively
 survey here, all olfactometers can be classified into a few basic types
 based on: 
