\begin_layout Standard
We define the following terms: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{c_{1}}$
\end_inset

and 
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{c_{2}}$
\end_inset

are the concentrations of odorant in gas phase in tube 1 (the Pasteur pipette)
