\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $w\theta_{1}$
\end_inset

and 
\begin_inset Formula $w\theta_{2}$
\end_inset

are the surface concentrations of odorants bound to tubes 1 and 2; 
\begin_inset Formula $w$
\end_inset

